## 📄 FILE #22 — `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`

```yaml
name: Deploy Storm-MD

on:
  push:
    branches: [main]
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v3
        with:
          node-version: '18'
      - run: npm install
      - run: echo "✅ Build successful"
